title: The Lone Ranger (Dynamite)
description:
The Lone Ranger is an unrelenting tale of the West. A young man searches for revenge, only to find justice... and that he's something greater than he ever thought he could be. 

Dynamite Entertainment's Lone Ranger series is a more mature telling of the story. Dark, gritty, and violent, this series takes the core of the legend and gives it a few new twists and turns.

Written by Brett Matthews and illustrated by Sergio Cariello, with covers by John Cassaday.


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
